Patch Set 2:

thank you @Jim for feedback.

@Ram, @Jim, if we stick with "name", can we remove the *instance* fields from status to remove confusion.  I don't think we know how to use them without being redundant.

@Mike - the hostname may change upon restart, in the case of the new pdp-x, it will in a k8s environment.   We need to make this assumption to be independent and play well moving forward with any changes that happen above in the kubernetes layer configuration.
